column16: Alex Dickerson singles on a sharp line drive to right fielder Hunter Pence.   Carlos Asuaje scores.    Wil Myers scores.    Ryan Schimpf to 3rd.
Ryan Schimpf walks.   Jon Jay scores.    Carlos Asuaje to 3rd.    Wil Myers to 2nd.
Matt Reynolds intentionally walks Wil Myers.
Carlos Asuaje doubles (2) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Denard Span.   Jon Jay to 3rd.
Jon Jay singles on a bunt ground ball to catcher Buster Posey.
Seung Hwan Oh strikes out swinging.
Kolten Wong out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Denard Span.   Jose Martinez scores.
Aledmys Diaz flies out to center fielder Denard Span.
Jose Martinez grounds out, second baseman Joe Panik to first baseman Brandon Belt.
Kolten Wong pops out to first baseman Brandon Belt in foul territory.

Padres challenged (play at 1st), call on the field was overturned: Alexi Amarista grounds into a force out, shortstop Brandon Crawford to second baseman Joe Panik.   Hector Sanchez out at 2nd.    Alexi Amarista to 1st.
Oswaldo Arcia called out on strikes.
Hector Sanchez singles on a line drive to center fielder Denard Span.
Ryan Schimpf flies out to center fielder Denard Span.
Alex Dickerson lines out to right fielder Hunter Pence.
Yangervis Solarte pops out to catcher Buster Posey in foul territory.
Jason Heyward singles on a line drive to center fielder Denard Span.   Anthony Rizzo scores.    Addison Russell to 2nd.
Matt Reynolds intentionally walks Addison Russell.
Ben Zobrist grounds out softly to first baseman Brandon Belt.   Anthony Rizzo to 2nd.
Anthony Rizzo singles on a line drive to left fielder Gorkys Hernandez.
Dexter Fowler pops out to first baseman Brandon Belt in foul territory.
Matt Szczur grounds out, shortstop Brandon Crawford to first baseman Brandon Belt.
David Ross grounds out, shortstop Brandon Crawford to first baseman Brandon Belt.
Javier Baez lines out to shortstop Brandon Crawford.
Ben Revere singles on a ground ball to center fielder Gregor Blanco.
Trea Turner grounds out, shortstop Brandon Crawford to first baseman Brandon Belt.   Bryce Harper to 3rd.
Ben Revere flies out to left fielder Angel Pagan.
